)@@G@@PG NUMBER   @E@@@@          +         0                 . CDE006: TYPE AIV
)@@G@@REA   @F@@@@          +         04230 . .         . CDE007: ALLOCATED PAIW
)@@G@@GES   @G@@@@          +         1 . .             . CDE008: SPACED OVERFIX
)@@G@@LOW PAGES   @F@@@@          +         023 . .           . CDE009: EVERY IY
)@@G@@DATA PAGES  @G@@@@          +         074 . .           . CDE010: AT ENDIZ
)@@G@@ OVERFLOW PAGES   @G@@@@          +         1 . .             . CDE011: JA
)@@G@@NUMBER OF CALC CHAINS   @[@@@@.     @B@@@@          $ASCII              JB
)@@G@@        .   @]@@@@IDE1* .     @B@@@@          $RES      2               JC
)@@G@@  .   @E@@@@          +         0                 . IDE001: RECORD CODE JD
)@@G@@@E@@@@          +         0                 . IDE002: ITEM CODE   @E@@@@JE
)@@G@@          +         077 . .           . IDE003: ITEM SIZE   @F@@@@      JF
)@@G@@    +         032 . .           . IDE004: START BIT OF ITEM @F@@@@      JG
)@@G@@    '-085367 ' . .              . IDE005: START OF ITEM TEXT@[@@@@.     JH
)@@G@@@]@@@@IDE2* .     @B@@@@          $RES      2                 .   @E@@@@JI
)@@G@@          +         0                 . IDE001: RECORD CODE @E@@@@      JJ
)@@G@@    +         0                 . IDE002: ITEM CODE   @E@@@@          + JK
)@@G@@        2*9               . IDE003: ITEM SIZE   @F@@@@          +       JL
)@@G@@  35                . IDE004: START BIT OF ITEM @F@@@@          '04--'  JM
)@@G@@                    . IDE005: START OF ITEM TEXT@[@@@@.     @]@@@@IDE3* JN
)@@G@@.     @B@@@@          $RES      2                 .   @E@@@@          + JO
)@@G@@        0                 . IDE001: RECORD CODE @E@@@@          +       JP
)@@G@@  0                 . IDE002: ITEM CODE   @E@@@@          +         2*9 JQ
)@@G@@              . IDE003: ITEM SIZE   @F@@@@          +         35        JR
)@@G@@        . IDE004: START BIT OF ITEM @F@@@@          '10--'              JS
)@@G@@        . IDE005: START OF ITEM TEXT@[@@@@.     @B@@@@PARAMS    +       JT
)@@G@@  IDE1              .   @B@@@@          +         IDE2              .   JU
)@@G@@@B@@@@          +         IDE3              .   @[@@@@$(1) .@]@@@@START JV
)@@G@@.     @C@@@@          SLJ       TON$              . SNOOPY  @[@@@@.     JW
)@@G@@@E@@@@          L         A0,(1,PARAMS)     . POINT TO PARAM AREA @D@@@@JX
)@@G@@          L         X2,(1,CDE)        . POINT TO CDE  @G@@@@          L JY
)@@G@@        X4,(9,CDEX)       . POINT TO CDE ENTRY FOR THIS AREA@F@@@@      JZ
)@@G@@    L         X3,0,*A0          . POINT TO FIRST IDE ENTRY  @B@@@@      KA
)@@G@@    LXI,U     X3,1              .   @[@@@@.     @G@@@@          LMJ     KB
)@@G@@  X11,ALCALC$$      . GO TO "ALCALC" ALTERNATE ENTRY  @F@@@@          L$KC
)@@G@@SNAP    $CFS('A6/A13'),2,0,$ . DUMP A6=PAGE, A13=CHAIN@B@@@@          ERKD
)@@G@@        EXIT$             .   @B@@@@          $END      START           KE
)@@G@@  .   _@@@@@        X2,(1,CDE)        . POINT TO CDE  @G@@@@          L KF
)@@G@@        X4,(9,CDEX)       . POINT TO CDE ENTRY FOR THIS AREA@F@@@@      KG
)@@G@@    L         X3,0,*A0  *[S@@@*SDFF*@E@@@@DISPLY: FORMAT 'KEY CALCS TO PKH
)@@G@@AGE ',D,', CHAIN ',D,'.',*    @A@@@@DIM:    FORMAT 'DIM KEY',D,'(',D,')'KI
)@@G@@@ @@@@PARAM:  FORMAT 'KEY',D,','    @ @@@@ANGLES: FORMAT '<KEY',D,'>,'  KJ
)@@G@@@#@@@@D:      FORMAT D  @B@@@@LET1:   FORMAT 'LET <X>=ASCII(<KEY',D,'>)'KK
)@@G@@@A@@@@LET2:   FORMAT 'LET <KEY',D,'>=<X>' @G@@@@IF:     FORMAT 'IF KEY',KL
)@@G@@D,'(1)=BLANKS AND KEY',D,'(2)=0 LET PROMPT?=1'  @B@@@@TREAD:  FORMAT R,'KM
)@@G@@TREAD <TRD>,<KEY',D,'>' @A@@@@RECNAM: FORMAT '/',<RRT[1]:S3>WA    @D@@@@KN
)@@G@@SLOT:   FORMAT '...RECORD POINTS TO PAGE SLOT ',D     @A@@@@OTHRPG: FORMKO
)@@G@@AT ' ON PAGE ',D,'.',*  @]@@@@        @   @G@@@@        DIM A$REA(10),R$KP
)@@G@@EC(10),REQKEY(23),CURKEY(23),X(23),B(3),TRD(2)  @ @@@@        LET BLANKSKQ
)@@G@@ = '      ' @]@@@@        @   @G@@@@        ERROR IGNERR                KR
)@@G@@   @ IGNORE "TOO MANY PARAMS" ERROR @H@@@@        PARAMETER <A$REA>,<R$EKS
)@@G@@C>       @ FETCH AREA & RECORD, IGNORE REST     @G@@@@IGNERR: ERROR ERR KT
)@@G@@                     @ HANDLE ALL ERRORS FROM HERE ON @F@@@@        IF AKU
)@@G@@$REA(1)<>'      ' AREA,N <A$REA> @ MAKE AREA CURRENT  @F@@@@        IF RKV
)@@G@@$EC(1)<>'      '  RECORD <R$EC>  @ MAKE RECORD CURRENT@G@@@@        LET KW
)@@G@@R$TYPE = RCODE             @ SAVE REQUESTED RECORD CODE     @]@@@@      KX
)@@G@@  @   @G@@@@        @ DYNAMICALLY GENERATE THE "DIMENSION" STATEMENT FORKY
)@@G@@ EACH KEY.  @]@@@@        @   @^@@@@        LET LONGST = 0  @E@@@@      KZ
)@@G@@  LET IDT^ = 014                 @ KEY IDT POINTER    @ @@@@        REPELA
)@@G@@AT KEY# = 1,1     @F@@@@          LET LEN = (RDT [IDT^+1]:H2 +35) / 36 @LB
)@@G@@ # WDS IN THIS KEY@F@@@@          IF LEN=1 LET LEN=2           @ MUST HALC
)@@G@@VE AT LEAST 2     @F@@@@          WRITE DIM KEY#,LEN           @ CREATE LD
)@@G@@"DIM" STATEMENT   @F@@@@          *                            @ EXECUTELE
)@@G@@ "DIM" STATEMENT  @D@@@@          LET IDT^ = IDT^ + 3          @ NEXT KELF
)@@G@@Y ITEM@A@@@@        UNTIL KEY# = RDT[010]:S6    @]@@@@        @   @H@@@@LG
)@@G@@        @ DYNAMICALLY GENERATE THE PARAMETER LIST CONTAINING THE AREA-SPLH
)@@G@@EC,   @G@@@@        @ RECORD-SPEC, AND THE PROPER NUMBER OF KEYS FOR THILI
)@@G@@S RECORD.   @]@@@@        @   @H@@@@        WRITE = ' PARAMETER <A$REA>,LJ
)@@G@@<R$EC>,' @ BEGIN "PARAMETER" STATEMENT    @ @@@@        REPEAT KEY# = 1,LK
)@@G@@1     @G@@@@          WRITE PARAM KEY#             @ ADD NEXT KEY TO PARLL
)@@G@@AMETER LIST @A@@@@        UNTIL KEY# = RDT[010]:S6    @ @@@@        WRITLM
)@@G@@E = X(-1),' '     @G@@@@        *                              @ GENERATLN
)@@G@@E "PARAMETER" STATEMENT @]@@@@        @   @F@@@@        @ IF ANY KEYS WELO
)@@G@@RE NOT SPECIFIED ON THE MACRO CALL, PROMPT@A@@@@        @ THE USER FOR TLP
)@@G@@HEM HERE.   @]@@@@        @   @E@@@@        LET IDT^ = 014              LQ
)@@G@@   @ KEY IDT POINTER    @ @@@@        REPEAT KEY# = 1,1     @F@@@@      LR
)@@G@@    LET PROMPT?=0                @ ASSUME WE WON'T PROMPT   @ @@@@      LS
)@@G@@    WRITE IF KEY#,KEY#  @H@@@@          *                            @ "LT
)@@G@@IF KEYN WASN'T GIVEN, LET PROMPT=1" @E@@@@          IF PROMPT? THEN     LU
)@@G@@         @ MUST PROMPT USER   @ @@@@            WRITE = 'KEY #'   @^@@@@LV
)@@G@@            WRITE D KEY#@^@@@@            WRITE = '?' @F@@@@            LW
)@@G@@LET <TRD>=WBUF(1,12)       @ COPY "KEYN?" TO <TRD>    @ @@@@            LX
)@@G@@WRITE TREAD KEY#  @E@@@@            *                          @ "TREAD LY
)@@G@@*,<KEYN>"   @#@@@@          END IF  @D@@@@          LET IDT^ = IDT^ + 3 LZ
)@@G@@         @ NEXT KEY ITEM@A@@@@        UNTIL KEY# = RDT[010]:S6    @]@@@@MA
)@@G@@        @   @E@@@@        @ CREATE <REQKEY>, THE CONCATENATED KEY REQUESMB
)@@G@@TED.  @]@@@@        @   @E@@@@        LET IDT^ = 014                 @ KMC
)@@G@@EY IDT POINTER    @E@@@@        LET REQKEY^ = 1                @ REQKEY MD
)@@G@@POINTER     @ @@@@        REPEAT KEY# = 1,1     @E@@@@          IF RDT[IME
)@@G@@DT^]:S2**020=020 THEN @ ITEM IS DISPLAY   @D@@@@            IF RDT[IDT^]MF
)@@G@@:S2**070=020 THEN @ ASCII     @A@@@@              LET BITSPERBYTE = 9   MG
)@@G@@@D@@@@            ELSE                       @ FIELDATA     @A@@@@      MH
)@@G@@        LET BITSPERBYTE = 6   @#@@@@            END IF@E@@@@            MI
)@@G@@LET NUMBYTES = RDT[IDT^+1]:H2 / BITSPERBYTE     @#@@@@            @     MJ
)@@G@@@ @@@@            REPEAT KEY^ = 1, 1@E@@@@COPY:   FORMAT 'LET [REQKEY:REMK
)@@G@@QKEY^,6]=[KEY',D,':KEY^,6]'   @ @@@@              WRITE COPY KEY# @H@@@@ML
)@@G@@              *                        @ COPY NEXT INPUT BYTE TO <REQKEYMM
)@@G@@>     @B@@@@              LET REQKEY^ = REQKEY^ + 1   @A@@@@            MN
)@@G@@UNTIL KEY^ = NUMBYTES   @C@@@@          ELSE                         @ CMO
)@@G@@OMP   @C@@@@            ???? @ DON'T KNOW WHAT TO DO NOW    @#@@@@      MP
)@@G@@    END IF  @D@@@@          LET IDT^ = IDT^ + 3          @ NEXT KEY ITEMMQ
)@@G@@@A@@@@        UNTIL KEY# = RDT[010]:S6    @F@@@@        REPEAT I=1,1    MR
)@@G@@               @ APPEND 5 MORE BLANKS     @B@@@@          LET [REQKEY:REMS
)@@G@@QKEY^+I,6]=' '    @#@@@@        UNTIL I=5 @]@@@@        @   @F@@@@      MT
)@@G@@  @ CONVERT ANY ASCII DISPLAY KEYS FROM FIELDATA TO ASCII   @]@@@@      MU
)@@G@@  @   @E@@@@        LET IDT^ = 014                 @ KEY IDT POINTER    MV
)@@G@@@ @@@@        REPEAT KEY# = 1,1     @E@@@@          IF RDT[IDT^]:S2**070MW
)@@G@@=020 THEN @ ASCII DISPLAY     @ @@@@            WRITE LET1 KEY#   @F@@@@MX
)@@G@@            *                         @ "LET <X>=ASCII(<KEYN>)"   @ @@@@MY
)@@G@@            WRITE LET2 KEY#   @E@@@@            *                       MZ
)@@G@@  @ "LET <KEYN>=<X>"    @#@@@@          END IF  @D@@@@          LET IDT^NA
)@@G@@ = IDT^ + 3          @ NEXT KEY ITEM@A@@@@        UNTIL KEY# = RDT[010]:NB
)@@G@@S6    @]@@@@        @   @F@@@@        WRITE = 'LET I=ALCALC$ '       @ BNC
)@@G@@EGIN "ALCALC$" CALL     @ @@@@        REPEAT KEY# = 1,1     @G@@@@      ND
)@@G@@    WRITE ANGLES KEY#            @ ADD NEXT KEY TO ALCALC$ CALL   @A@@@@NE
)@@G@@        UNTIL KEY# = RDT[010]:S6    @ @@@@        WRITE = X(-1),' '     NF
)@@G@@@D@@@@        *                              @ CALL ALCALC$ @ @@@@      NG
)@@G@@  WRITE DISPLY I:H1,I:H2@]@@@@        @   @D@@@@        IF RDT[014]:S2**NH
)@@G@@020<>0 THEN @ NON-COMP ITEM   @C@@@@          IF RDT[014]:S2**070=020 THNI
)@@G@@EN @ ASCII  @A@@@@            LET <X>=ASCII(<CURKEY>) @ @@@@            NJ
)@@G@@LET <CURKEY>=<X>  @C@@@@            LET WDSINKEY=(3+RDT[015]:H2/9)/4    NK
)@@G@@@D@@@@          ELSE                         @ FIELDATA     @C@@@@      NL
)@@G@@      LET WDSINKEY=(5+RDT[015]:H2/6)/6    @#@@@@          END IF  @^@@@@NM
)@@G@@        ELSE @ COMP ITEM@ @@@@          LET BYTESPERWD=36/V @D@@@@      NN
)@@G@@    LET WDSINKEY=(5+RDT[016]:S2)/BYTESPERWD     @#@@@@        END IF    NO
)@@G@@@]@@@@        @   @B@@@@        LET HDRDBP=ENCODE(ACODE,I:H1,I:H2)@ @@@@NP
)@@G@@        LET CURDBP=HDRDBP     @]@@@@        @   @]@@@@NEWREC: @   @^@@@@NQ
)@@G@@        FIND CURDBP     @E@@@@        IF RESULT=0 WRITE,S = '*** RECORD NR
)@@G@@NOT FOUND ***',*  @ @@@@        RECORD PAGE[$]:NT1    @E@@@@        IF RNS
)@@G@@$TYPE<>RCODE GOTO NOT-IT   @ WRONG RECORD TYPE  @]@@@@        @   @E@@@@NT
)@@G@@        LET IDT^ = 014                 @ KEY IDT POINTER    @ @@@@      NU
)@@G@@  REPEAT KEY# = 1,1     @^@@@@      @   WRITE = '"'   @F@@@@          EXNV
)@@G@@TRACTKEY $,IDT^            @ COPY KEY VALUE INTO WBUF @D@@@@      @   WRNW
)@@G@@ITE = '",'                 @ DELIMIT KEYS @D@@@@          LET IDT^ = IDTNX
)@@G@@^ + 3          @ NEXT KEY ITEM@A@@@@        UNTIL KEY# = RDT[010]:S6    NY
)@@G@@@E@@@@      @ WRITE = X(-1)                  @ ERASE JUNK AT END  @ @@@@NZ
)@@G@@        LET <CURKEY>=WBUF()   @^@@@@        REPEAT I=1,1    @C@@@@      OA
)@@G@@    IF REQKEY(I)<>CURKEY(I) GOTO NOT-IT   @^@@@@        UNTIL I=WDSINKEYOB
)@@G@@@#@@@@        WRITE = R @#@@@@        DUMPREC   @#@@@@        RETURN    OC
)@@G@@@]@@@@        @   @]@@@@NOT-IT: @   @A@@@@        LET C = $ + RDT[5]:H2 OD
)@@G@@- 1   @G@@@@        IF ART[3]:B35=1 LET C=C-1 @ IF CALC PRIOR LINKS, BACOE
)@@G@@K UP 1 WORD @ @@@@        LET CURDBP=PAGE[C]    @B@@@@        WRITE RECNOF
)@@G@@AM <RRT:010,7+RRT[1]:S3>@ @@@@        IF CURDBP=HDRDBP THEN @F@@@@      OG
)@@G@@    WRITE = '...RECORD POINTS BACK TO CALC CHAIN HEADER.',* @C@@@@      OH
)@@G@@    WRITE = '*** RECORD NOT FOUND ***',*  @#@@@@          RETURN  @#@@@@OI
)@@G@@        END IF    @ @@@@        LET <B>=DECODE(CURDBP)@^@@@@        WRITOJ
)@@G@@E SLOT B(3) @ @@@@        IF B(2)=PGNUM THEN    @A@@@@          WRITE = OK
)@@G@@' ON THIS PAGE.',*@]@@@@        ELSE@ @@@@          WRITE OTHRPG B(2)   OL
)@@G@@@#@@@@        END IF    @^@@@@        GOTO NEWREC     @]@@@@        @   OM
)@@G@@@#@@@@ERR:    ERROR     @#@@@@        ERRPR     @#@@@@        RETURN    ON
)@@G@@@]@@@@        @   @C@@@@GIGO:   WRITE = 'CALC KEY MUST BE NUMERIC.',*   OO
)@@G@@@#@@@@        RETURN    @]@@@@        @   @ @@@@ERR???: WRITE = '<ALCALCOP
)@@G@@> '   @#@@@@        ERRPR,W   @#@@@@        WRITE *   @]@@@@        STOPOQ
)@@G@@_@@@@@    @ # ALLOCATED PAGES @D@@@@ PATCH 17,H2*[S@@@*SDFF*@B@@@@DIM:  OR
)@@G@@  FORMAT ' DIM KEY',D,'(',D,')'     @ @@@@PARAM:  FORMAT 'KEY',D,','    OS
)@@G@@@]@@@@        @   @G@@@@        DIM DIV(3)                     @ USED FOOT
)@@G@@R DIVISION RESULTS, ETC.@]@@@@        @   @G@@@@        ERROR ERR       OU
)@@G@@               @ HANDLE ALL ERRORS FROM HERE ON @]@@@@        @   @G@@@@OV
)@@G@@        @ DYNAMICALLY GENERATE THE "DIMENSION" STATEMENT FOR EACH KEY.  OW
)@@G@@@H@@@@        @ WHILE DOING THIS, ALSO DETERMINE THE LENGTH OF THE LONGEOX
)@@G@@ST KEY.     @]@@@@        @   @^@@@@        LET LONGST = 0  @E@@@@      OY
)@@G@@  LET IDT^ = 014                 @ KEY IDT POINTER    @ @@@@        REPEOZ
)@@G@@AT KEY# = 1,1     @F@@@@          LET LEN = (RDT [IDT^+1]:H2 +35) / 36 @PA
)@@G@@ # WDS IN THIS KEY@F@@@@          WRITE DIM KEY#,LEN           @ CREATE PB
)@@G@@"DIM" STATEMENT   @F@@@@          *                            @ EXECUTEPC
)@@G@@ "DIM" STATEMENT  @E@@@@          IF LEN > LONGST LET LONGST = LEN @ FINPD
)@@G@@D LONGEST   @D@@@@          LET IDT^ = IDT^ + 3          @ NEXT KEY ITEMPE
)@@G@@@A@@@@        UNTIL KEY# = RDT[010]:S6    @H@@@@        DIM KEY(LONGST+1PF
)@@G@@)              @ CREATE "KEY" 1 LONGER THAN LONGEST   @]@@@@        @   PG
)@@G@@@F@@@@        @ DYNAMICALLY GENERATE THE PARAMETER LIST CONTAINING THE  PH
)@@G@@@C@@@@        @ PROPER NUMBER OF KEYS FOR THIS RECORD.@]@@@@        @   PI
)@@G@@@G@@@@        WRITE = ' PARAMETER '          @ BEGIN "PARAMETER" STATEMEPJ
)@@G@@NT    @ @@@@        REPEAT KEY# = 1,1     @G@@@@          WRITE PARAM KEPK
)@@G@@Y#             @ ADD NEXT KEY TO PARAMETER LIST @A@@@@        UNTIL KEY#PL
)@@G@@ = RDT[010]:S6    @ @@@@        WRITE = X(-1),' '     @G@@@@        *   PM
)@@G@@                           @ GENERATE "PARAMETER" STATEMENT @]@@@@      PN
)@@G@@  @   @A@@@@        @ DEFINE CDE PACKET VALUES  @]@@@@        @   @H@@@@PO
)@@G@@        LET WIN^ = RDT[3]:H2           @ POINTER TO "WITHIN" ENTRIES IN PP
)@@G@@RDT   @F@@@@        LET CDE004 = 0                 @ ASSUME NO LOWER BOUPQ
)@@G@@ND    @F@@@@        LET CDE005 = 0                 @    AND NO UPPER BOUPR
)@@G@@ND    @G@@@@        IF RDT[WIN^]:S2 LET CDE004 = RDT[WIN^+1]:H1 @ LOWER PS
)@@G@@BOUND PG #  @G@@@@        IF RDT[WIN^]:S3 LET CDE005 = RDT[WIN^+1]:H2 @ PT
)@@G@@UPPER BOUND PG #  @E@@@@        LET CDE007 = ART[010]:H1       @ # ALLOCPU
)@@G@@ATED PAGES  @F@@@@        LET CDE008 = ART[020]:H1       @ # SPACED OVERPV
)@@G@@FLOW PAGES  @E@@@@        LET CDE009 = ART[010]:H2       @ # EVERY DATA PW
)@@G@@PAGES @F@@@@        LET CDE010 = ART[020]:H2       @ # AT END OVERFLOW PPX
)@@G@@AGES  @D@@@@        LET CDE011 = ART[023]:H2       @ # CALC CHAINS@D@@@@PY
)@@G@@        LET CDE012 = RDT[010]:S6       @ # CALC KEYS  @]@@@@        @   PZ
)@@G@@@F@@@@        @ COMPUTE THE NUMBER OF PRIME PAGES WE HAVE AVAILABLE     QA
)@@G@@@]@@@@        @   @E@@@@        IF CDE004 = 0 THEN             @ NO WITHQB
)@@G@@IN CLAUSE   @F@@@@          LET A2 = CDE007 - CDE010     @ # ALLOC PGS -QC
)@@G@@ AT END O/F @G@@@@CONTA:    LET A4 = CDE009 + CDE008     @ # CONSEC PRIMQD
)@@G@@E + # INTER O/F   @F@@@@          LET A2 = A2 / A4             @ # GROUPQE
)@@G@@S IS NOW IN A2    @G@@@@          LET A2 = A2 * CDE009 * CDE011 @ A2 = #QF
)@@G@@ PRIME CHAINS TO HASH TO@ @@@@        ELSE @ WITHIN CLAUSE  @E@@@@      QG
)@@G@@    LET A2 = CDE009              @ # CONSEC PRIME PGS @F@@@@          LEQH
)@@G@@T A3 = A2 + CDE008         @ + INTER O/F = GROUP SIZE @G@@@@          LEQI
)@@G@@T A4 = CDE004 / A3         @ COMPUTE # GROUPS BELOW LOWER PG@B@@@@      QJ
)@@G@@    LET A5 = CDE004 \ A3         @  @G@@@@          IF A5 > A2 LET A5 = QK
)@@G@@A2       @ IF OVERGRP > CONSEC, USE CONSEC@F@@@@          LET A14 = A4  QL
)@@G@@               @ SAVE # GROUPS FOR LATER  @F@@@@          LET A15 = A5  QM
)@@G@@               @ SAVE # OVERGRPS FOR LATER@]@@@@          @ @E@@@@      QN
)@@G@@    LET A2 = A2 - A5             @ # PGS IN INTERVAL  @E@@@@          LEQO
)@@G@@T A4 = CDE005 / A3         @ COMPUTE # GROUPS   @B@@@@          LET A5 =QP
)@@G@@ CDE005 \ A3         @  @D@@@@          LET A3 = CDE009              @ #QQ
)@@G@@ CONSEC DATA@G@@@@          IF A5 > A3 LET A5 = A3       @ IF OVERGRP > QR
)@@G@@CONSEC, USE CONSEC@G@@@@          LET A4 = A4 - A14 - 1        @ COMPUTEQS
)@@G@@ # GRPS IN INTERVAL     @G@@@@          @ # PRIME IN INTERVAL + O/F ON TQT
)@@G@@OP + O/F ON BOTTOM = # CHAINS @D@@@@          LET A2 = ((A4 * CDE009) + QU
)@@G@@A2 + A5) * CDE011 @#@@@@        END IF    @]@@@@        @   @I@@@@      QV
)@@G@@  LET A2 = PRIMER A2             @ GET CLOSEST PRIME TO # PRIME DATA CHNQW
)@@G@@S     @]@@@@        @   @G@@@@        @ NOW: A2 = # OF CALC CHAINS TO BEQX
)@@G@@ USED IN THE CALC ROUTINE     @B@@@@        @      R1 WILL = # KEYS TO PQY
)@@G@@ROCESS@E@@@@        @      R2 WILL = # WDS IN CURRENT KEY TO PROCESS    QZ
)@@G@@@]@@@@        @   @E@@@@        LET A5 = 0                     @ ZERO UPRA
)@@G@@PER ACCUM   @E@@@@        LET R1 = CDE012 - 1            @ # CALC KEYS -RB
)@@G@@ 1    @G@@@@        IF CDE012 = 0 WRITE,S = '<ALCALC> RECORD CONTAINS NORC
)@@G@@ CALC KEY',*@]@@@@        @   @F@@@@        @ COMPUTE # WDS IN KEY AND #RD
)@@G@@ CHARS IN LAST WORD OF KEY.   @G@@@@        @ REMEMBER, THE KEY DOES NOTRE
)@@G@@ HAVE TO FALL ON A WD BOUNDARY.     @]@@@@        @   @E@@@@        LET RF
)@@G@@IDT^ = 014                 @ PTR TO 1ST CALC IDT@^@@@@        LET KEY# =RG
)@@G@@ 0    @]@@@@        @   @F@@@@        @ READ THE NEXT KEY IN & SHIFT IT RH
)@@G@@TO ITS PROPER POSITION  @]@@@@        @   @E@@@@NEWKEY: LET KEY# = KEY# RI
)@@G@@+1             @ BUMP KEY NUMBER    @]@@@@        @   @E@@@@        LET RJ
)@@G@@IDE003 = RDT [IDT^+1]:H2   @ IDE003: ITEM SIZE  @F@@@@        LET IDE004RK
)@@G@@ = RDT [IDT^]:S3     @ IDE004: START BIT OF ITEM@]@@@@        @   @E@@@@RL
)@@G@@        LET NUMBYTES = IDE003 / 9      @ # BYTES IN KEY     @F@@@@      RM
)@@G@@  LET SHIFTER = (35 - IDE004) / 9 @ # BYTES TO SHIFT RIGHT  @G@@@@      RN
)@@G@@  REPEAT I = NUMBYTES, -1        @ COPY FROM END TO BEGINNING     @E@@@@RO
)@@G@@COPY:  FORMAT 'LET [KEY: I+SHIFTER, 9] = [KEY',D,': I, 9]'  @ @@@@      RP
)@@G@@    WRITE COPY KEY#     @F@@@@          *                            @ CRQ
)@@G@@OPY KEYN BYTE TO KEY    @^@@@@        UNTIL I = 1     @]@@@@        @   RR
)@@G@@@E@@@@        LET X3 = 1                     @ INDEX INTO KEY     @E@@@@RS
)@@G@@        LET A3 = IDE003 / 9            @ # CHARS IN KEY     @H@@@@      RT
)@@G@@  LET A10 = 35 - IDE004          @ 1ST BIT POSITION (FROM 0, L TO R)    RU
)@@G@@@E@@@@        LET X7 = A10                   @ SAVE FOR LATER     @F@@@@RV
)@@G@@        LET A10 = A10 / 9              @ COMPUTE # CHARS OFFS     @F@@@@RW
)@@G@@        LET A3 = A3 + A10              @ ADD TO # CHARS IN THE WD @F@@@@RX
)@@G@@        LET A4 = A3 \ 4                @ COMPUTE # CHARS REMAINING@D@@@@RY
)@@G@@        LET A3 = A3 / 4                @   AND # WORDS@D@@@@        IF ARZ
)@@G@@4 = 0 THEN                 @ NO REMAINDER @G@@@@          LET A3 = A3 - SA
)@@G@@1              @ DECREASE TO MAKE LOOP WORK     @G@@@@          LET A4 =SB
)@@G@@ 4                   @ & SET 4 CHARS IN LAST WD COUNT @#@@@@        END SC
)@@G@@IF    @]@@@@        @   @ @@@@        @ A3 = # CHARS IN KEY @A@@@@      SD
)@@G@@  @ A4 = # CHARS IN LAST WORD @F@@@@        @ THE 1ST WD OF KEY REQUIRESSE
)@@G@@ SPECIAL ATTENTION BECAUSE    @C@@@@        @ IT MAY NOT START ON A WORDSF
)@@G@@ BOUNDARY.  @]@@@@        @   @E@@@@REMAIN: LET R2 = A3                 SG
)@@G@@   @ # CHARS TO PROCESS @F@@@@        LET A6 = KEY(X3)               @ GSH
)@@G@@ET 1ST WD TO PROCESS    @E@@@@        LET X3 = X3 + 1                @ ISI
)@@G@@NCREMENT POINTER  @^@@@@        IF X7>0 THEN    @H@@@@          PWORD J1SJ
)@@G@@ 35,X7               @ J-DESIG OF UNUSED BITS IN 1ST WD     @E@@@@      SK
)@@G@@    LET A6:J1 = 0                @ CLEAR UNUSED PART  @#@@@@        END SL
)@@G@@IF    @ @@@@        IF R2 = 0 GOTO ONEWRD @#@@@@        LET R3 = 1@C@@@@SM
)@@G@@        LET R2 = R2 - 1                @ (JGD)  @E@@@@        IF R2 >= 0SN
)@@G@@ GOTO HASH1          @ GO HASH THIS WORD  @G@@@@HASH:   LET A5 = A6     SO
)@@G@@               @ REMAINDER FROM LAST DIVIDE     @F@@@@        LET A6 = KSP
)@@G@@EY(X3)               @ GET NEXT WD TO PROCESS   @E@@@@        LET X3 = XSQ
)@@G@@3 + 1                @ INCREMENT POINTER  @F@@@@HASH1:  LET A7 = A6 ** 1SR
)@@G@@               @ LOW BIT KEYWORD TO A7    @G@@@@        LET <DIV> = DSL SS
)@@G@@A5,A6,1        @ DOUBLE SHIFT A5/A6 1 BIT RIGHT @H@@@@        LET <DIV> ST
)@@G@@= DIVIDE DIV(1),DIV(2),A2 @ 2-WORD DIVISION: A5&A6 / A2     @G@@@@      SU
)@@G@@  LET A5 = DIV(2)                @ LOW WORD OF INTEGER RESULT     @D@@@@SV
)@@G@@        LET A6 = DIV(3)                @ REMAINDER    @G@@@@        LET SW
)@@G@@A6 = A6 * 2 + A7           @ 0<A6<#CALC CHAINS, ADD LOW BIT @H@@@@      SX
)@@G@@  IF A6 >= A2 LET A6 = A6 - A2   @ IF TOO LARGE, DECREASE BY # CHAINS   SY
)@@G@@@F@@@@        IF R3 = 0 GOTO KEYDUN          @ IF DONE WITH THIS KEY    SZ
)@@G@@@C@@@@        LET R2 = R2 - 1                @ (JGD)  @F@@@@        IF RTA
)@@G@@2 >= 0 GOTO HASH           @ DO THE REST OF THE KEY   @]@@@@        @   TB
)@@G@@@D@@@@        @ WE HAVE DONE ALL WORDS IN THE KEY EXCEPT THE@D@@@@      TC
)@@G@@  @ LAST ONE. THIS WORD TAKES SPECIAL ATTENTION @C@@@@        @ BECAUSE TD
)@@G@@IT MAY BE A PARTIAL WORD.     @]@@@@        @   @G@@@@        LET A5 = ATE
)@@G@@6                    @ GET REMAINDER FROM LAST DIVIDE @D@@@@        LET TF
)@@G@@A6 = KEY(X3)               @ GET LAST WORD@G@@@@ONEWRD: LET R3 = 0      TG
)@@G@@               @ SHOW THAT THIS IS THE LAST WORD@F@@@@        LET <DIV> TH
)@@G@@= DSL A5,A6,(4-A4)*9 @ DOUBLE SHIFT A5/A6 RIGHT @^@@@@        LET A5=DIVTI
)@@G@@(1)   @^@@@@        LET A6=DIV(2)   @F@@@@        GOTO HASH1            TJ
)@@G@@         @ AND GO TO HASH FINAL WORD@]@@@@        @   @E@@@@        @ WHTK
)@@G@@EN CONTROL PASSES HERE, THE CURRENT KEY HAS     @^@@@@        @ BEEN HASTL
)@@G@@HED.  @]@@@@        @   @C@@@@KEYDUN: LET R1 = R1 - 1                @ (TM
)@@G@@JGD)  @G@@@@        IF R1 < 0 GOTO ALLDUN          @ GO TO ALLDUN IF NO TN
)@@G@@MORE KEYS   @G@@@@        LET IDT^ = IDT^ + 3            @ BUMP TO NEXT TO
)@@G@@CALC IDT ENTRY    @E@@@@        LET A5 = A6                    @ PUT RESTP
)@@G@@ULT IN A5   @G@@@@        GOTO NEWKEY                    @ AND GO HANDLETQ
)@@G@@ THIS NEW KEY     @]@@@@        @   @E@@@@ALLDUN: @ ALL KEYS HAVE BEEN HTR
)@@G@@ASHED AND WE HAVE A VALID     @D@@@@        @ CHAIN NUMBER IN A6. WE MUSTS
)@@G@@T COMPUTE THE PAGE@D@@@@        @ NUMBER AND THE CHAIN NUMBER FOR THIS KTT
)@@G@@EY.   @]@@@@        @   @C@@@@        LET A13 = A6 \ CDE011          @ CTU
)@@G@@HAIN #@C@@@@        LET A6 = A6 / CDE011           @ PAGE # @E@@@@      TV
)@@G@@  IF A6 = 0 LET A6 = 1           @ IF PG = 0, USE 1   @]@@@@        @   TW
)@@G@@@D@@@@        @ A6 CONTAINS A RELATIVE PAGE NUMBER. WE MUST @D@@@@      TX
)@@G@@  @ MAP THIS RELATIVE PAGE # BACK INTO THE VALID@D@@@@        @ PAGE SPATY
)@@G@@CE SUCH THAT THE PAGE WILL NOT FALL @B@@@@        @ INTO THE INTERSPERSETZ
)@@G@@D OVERFLOW. @]@@@@        @   @G@@@@        IF CDE004 > 0 THEN          UA
)@@G@@          @ WITHIN CLAUSE SPECIFIED @H@@@@          LET A6 = A6 + (A14 *UB
)@@G@@ CDE009) + A15  @ PRIME IN GRP + REL PG + EXCESS@#@@@@        END IF    UC
)@@G@@@]@@@@        @   @H@@@@        IF A6 >= CDE009 THEN           @ DOESN'TUD
)@@G@@ FALL INTO FIRST CONS DATA PGS@]@@@@          @ @E@@@@          @ HERE WUE
)@@G@@E PERFORM THE MAPPING OF THE RELATIVE     @D@@@@          @ PG NUMBERS TUF
)@@G@@O A VALID PG NOT FALLING INTO @A@@@@          @ INTERSPERSED OVERFLOW.  UG
)@@G@@@]@@@@          @ @E@@@@          LET A7 = A6 \ CDE009           @ # OVEUH
)@@G@@RGROUPS     @D@@@@          LET A6 = A6 / CDE009           @ # GROUP    UI
)@@G@@@E@@@@          IF A7=0 LET A7 =  - CDE008     @ HAVE TO BACK UP  @G@@@@UJ
)@@G@@          LET A6 = ((CDE009 + CDE008)  * A6) + A7 @ PGS IN GRP + O/F    UK
)@@G@@@#@@@@        END IF    @]@@@@        @   @F@@@@RETURN: LET RSLT:H1 = A6UL
)@@G@@               @ PAGE NUMBER SELECTED     @F@@@@        LET RSLT:H2 = A1UM
)@@G@@3              @ CHAIN NUMBER SELECTED    @]@@@@        @   @^@@@@      UN
)@@G@@  RETURN RSLT     @]@@@@        @   @ @@@@ERR:    WRITE = '<ALCALC> '   UO
)@@G@@@#@@@@        ERRPR,W   @#@@@@        WRITE *   @]@@@@        STOP_@@@@@UP
)@@G@@CD@@^U[@@@@W@@,)#9@)C@ZK@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@F[@@^U[@@@@C@@,*#'@ZS@@@UQ
)@@G@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@F[@@^W[@0@@=@@,0#;@Z)@@E@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@UR
)@@G@@*[S@@@*SDFF*@G@@@@ @ DIVIDES 2 WD INPUT BY 1 WD INPUT, GIVING 2 WD RESULUS
)@@G@@T + 1 WD REMAINDER@E@@@@        PARAMETER A,B,C               @ PRODUCESUT
)@@G@@ AB / C     @ @@@@        DIM TOP(2),RSLT(3)    @E@@@@        LET TOP(1)UU
)@@G@@=A                  @ 1ST HALF OF DIVIDEND@E@@@@        LET TOP(2)=B    UV
)@@G@@              @ 2ND HALF OF DIVIDEND@^@@@@        LET REMAIN=0    @D@@@@UW
)@@G@@        REPEAT D=1,1                  @ DIGIT NUMBER  @H@@@@          LEUX
)@@G@@T X=[TOP:D,1] + REMAIN    @ LOAD NEXT DIGIT + PREVIOUS REMAINDER  @D@@@@UY
)@@G@@          LET [RSLT:D,1]=X/C          @ INTEGER RESULT@E@@@@          LEUZ
)@@G@@T REMAIN=(X\C)*/1         @ CARRY REMAINDER     @#@@@@        UNTIL D=72VA
)@@G@@@F@@@@        LET RSLT(3)=REMAIN*/-1        @ FINAL REMAINDER TO WORD 3 VB
)@@G@@@^@@@@        RETURN  <RSLT>  _@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@VC
)@@G@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@*[S@@@*SDFF*@F@@@@      VD
)@@G@@  @ SHIFTS 2 WD INPUT (AB) BY C BITS, GIVING 2 WD RESULT    @^@@@@      VE
)@@G@@  DIM RSLT(3)     @E@@@@        PARAMETER A,B,C               @ PRODUCESVF
)@@G@@ AB */ -C   @G@@@@        IF C>71 THEN                  @ SHIFTED THE WHVG
)@@G@@OLE THING OUT     @^@@@@          LET RSLT(1)=0 @^@@@@          LET RSLTVH
)@@G@@(2)=0 @E@@@@        ELSE IF C=0 THEN              @ NO SHIFT AT ALL     VI
)@@G@@@^@@@@          LET RSLT(1)=A @^@@@@          LET RSLT(2)=B @D@@@@      VJ
)@@G@@  ELSE                          @ VALID SHIFT   @^@@@@          PWORD J7VK
)@@G@@ C-1,C@^@@@@          PWORD J8 35,C @ @@@@          PWORD J9 35,36-C    VL
)@@G@@@G@@@@          LET RSLT(2)=B:J9            @ SHIFT 2ND WORD RIGHT "C" BVM
)@@G@@ITS   @G@@@@          LET RSLT(2):J8=A:J7         @ SHIFT "C" BITS FROM VN
)@@G@@WD 1 TO WD 2@G@@@@          LET RSLT(1)=A:J9            @ SHIFT 1ST WORDVO
)@@G@@ RIGHT "C" BITS   @#@@@@        END IF    @]@@@@        @   @^@@@@      VP
)@@G@@  LET RSLT(3)=C   @^@@@@        RETURN  <RSLT>  _@@@@@"C" BITS FROM WD 1VQ
)@@G@@ TO WD 2    @G@@@@          LET RSLT(1)=A:J9    *[S@@[*SDFF*@^@@@@^[0GD2VR
)@@G@@GD!G(4G(2^[-AK)^@)@C@@@@^[(G0)GC2F)2B*0^[4H[>H0)C@)G-(I1(IT(GL?G*)GL9^@2VS
)@@G@@@H@@@@^@)HD&^[-AK/B*1AC)G9\I-\^[=H9,G*)C@)HD&^@1AC)H92^[?G(3IS?^[7G*$IL>VT
)@@G@@^[=H9,G*)^@)@E@@@@^@)H->I))GC2B(-AK!AC)C@)G(?HD!HD,GD4G*)AK)GD3^[-^[=HD6VU
)@@G@@HD3H92@]@@@@^[>H1=^[(G0)@C@@@@^[(G0)GC2F)3B*0^[4H[>H0)C@)G-(I1(IT(GL?G*)VV
)@@G@@GL9^@3@H@@@@^@)HD&^[-AK/B*3AK)G9\I-\^[=H9,G*)C@)HD&^@3AK)H92^[?G(3IS?^[7VW
)@@G@@G*$IL>^[=H9,G*)^@)@E@@@@^@)H->I))GC2B(-AK!AK)C@)G(?HD!HD,GD4G*)AS)GD3^[-VX
)@@G@@^[=HD6HD3H92@]@@@@^[>H1=^[(G0)@C@@@@^[(G0)GC2F)5B*0^[4H[>H0)C@)G-(I1(IT(VY
)@@G@@GL?G*)GL9^@5@H@@@@^@)HD&^[-AK/B*6A))G9\I-\^[=H9,G*)C@)HD&^@6A))H92^[?G(3VZ
)@@G@@IS?^[7G*$IL>^[=H9,G*)^@)@E@@@@^@)H->I))GC2B(-AK!A0)C@)G(?HD!HD,GD4G*)A0)WA
)@@G@@GD3^[-^[=HD6HD3H92@]@@@@^[>H1=^[(G0)@C@@@@^[(G0)GC2F)7B*0^[4H[>H0)C@)G-(WB
)@@G@@I1(IT(GL?G*)GL9^@7@H@@@@^@)HD&^[-AK/B*3A@0^[$H94H8)G-\H1>^[@^[(G0)AS0A@)WC
)@@G@@H92^[?G(3IS?^[7G*$IL>^[=H9,G*)@F@@@@^@)H->I))GC2B(-AK!AS0^[@^[>H-(H((H1-WD
)@@G@@I->^@7^[-IS)GC)G-(I1(IT\IK)^@)@]@@@@^[>H1=^[(G0)@^@@@@G-\H1>BK)IL>I-5IL,WE
)@@G@@^[-AK)_@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@*[S@@@*SDFF*@G@@@@TITLE:WF
)@@G@@  FORMAT *(-0),C44,'SIZE REPORT SUMMARY FOR SCHEMA "',<2>WF,'"'   @E@@@@WG
)@@G@@DATIM:  FORMAT C116,F2,'/',F2,'/',F2,' AT ',F2,':',F2,*,*3  @ @@@@ALINE:WH
)@@G@@  FORMAT <NWORDS>F6,*   @A@@@@AINFO:  FORMAT <2>WF,C15,D4,C21     @^@@@@WI
)@@G@@DEC:    FORMAT F6,D,*   @#@@@@TDFORM: FORMAT WF @A@@@@FILE:   FORMAT 'DBWJ
)@@G@@E*SRSAVE(-',D,').'@B@@@@OPEN:   FORMAT 'OPENING FILE ',<6>WF,*    @B@@@@WK
)@@G@@CLOSE:  FORMAT 'CLOSING FILE ',<6>WF,*    @D@@@@BADOPN: FORMAT 'ERROR ONWL
)@@G@@ OPEN OF FILE ',<6>WF,'  '    @B@@@@FACREJ: FORMAT 'FAC STATUS: ',O12,'.WM
)@@G@@  '   @]@@@@        @   @ @@@@        PARAMETER MAXCYCLES:9 @G@@@@      WN
)@@G@@  IF MAXCYCLES>9 WRITE,S = '<SRDUMP> TOO MANY CYCLES REQUESTED.',*@]@@@@WO
)@@G@@        @   @G@@@@        DIM A$CODE(1), P$RIME(2), O$FLOW(3), D$ATE(1),WP
)@@G@@ T$IME(1), FILE(6)@D@@@@        DIM ABITS((SCRT[010]:H1+5)/6) @ 1 BIT/ARWQ
)@@G@@EA    @E@@@@        DIM DATA(MAXCYCLES,SCRT[010]:H1), TD(MAXCYCLES,2)   WR
)@@G@@@]@@@@        @   @C@@@@        LET CYCX=0 @ ACTUAL CYCLES AVAILABLE    WS
)@@G@@@D@@@@        REPEAT CYC# = 1, 1 @ LOOP THRU BACK CYCLES    @E@@@@      WT
)@@G@@    WRITE FILE MAXCYCLES-CYC# @ CREATE ACTUAL FILENAME@ @@@@          LEWU
)@@G@@T <FILE>=WBUF()   @A@@@@          WRITE = R @ CLEAR WBUF NOW@B@@@@      WV
)@@G@@    IF OPTS:Z WRITE OPEN <FILE>     @D@@@@          LET OPNERR=0 @ SHOW WW
)@@G@@WE HAVEN'T ERRORED YET  @^@@@@          ERROR OPNERR  @A@@@@          OPWX
)@@G@@EN SDFI $$SR$$=<FILE>   @#@@@@OPNRET:   ERROR   @B@@@@          IF OPNERWY
)@@G@@R THEN @ ERROR ON OPEN  @A@@@@            WRITE BADOPN <FILE>     @D@@@@WZ
)@@G@@            IF FAC<0 WRITE FACREJ FAC @ FAC REJECT    @B@@@@            XA
)@@G@@WRITE = 'FILE IGNORED.',*     @^@@@@          ELSE @ OPEN OK@A@@@@      XB
)@@G@@      LET CYCX = CYCX + 1     @E@@@@            LET GOT$TD=0 @ SHOW WE DXC
)@@G@@ON'T HAVE TIME/DATE YET @^@@@@            DO FOREVER  @B@@@@            XD
)@@G@@  GET $$SR$$ (EOF=RDDONE)     @C@@@@              IF NWORDS=015 THEN @ RXE
)@@G@@IGHT LENGTH @J@@@@                IF GOT$TD=0 AND IOBUF[0]='SIZE R' AND XF
)@@G@@IOBUF[1]='EPORT ' THEN @ FOUND T/D  @E@@@@                  REPEAT I=1,1XG
)@@G@@ @ LOAD DATE INTO <D$ATE>     @D@@@@                    LET [D$ATE:I,6] XH
)@@G@@= [IOBUF:47+I,6]  @D@@@@                    LET [T$IME:I,6] = [IOBUF:56+XI
)@@G@@I,6]  @ @@@@                  UNTIL I=5   @E@@@@                  LET GOXJ
)@@G@@T$TD=1 @ SHOW WE'VE GOT TIME/DATE   @F@@@@                  LET TD(CYCX,XK
)@@G@@1)=D$ATE(1) @ SAVE DATE IN <TD>     @F@@@@                  LET TD(CYCX,XL
)@@G@@2)=T$IME(1) @ SAVE TIME IN <TD>     @B@@@@                ELSE @ NOT TIMXM
)@@G@@E/DATE LINE @F@@@@                  LET OK? = IOBUF[0]:S1<>' ' AND IOBUFXN
)@@G@@[2]:S1=' '  @D@@@@                  LET OK? = OK? AND IOBUF[3]:S1=' '   XO
)@@G@@@C@@@@                  IF OK? THEN @ GOT A WINNER    @^@@@@            XP
)@@G@@        @   @F@@@@                    REPEAT I=1,1 @ LOAD AREA CODE INTOXQ
)@@G@@ <A$CODE>   @E@@@@                      LET [A$CODE:I,6] = [IOBUF:13+I,6XR
)@@G@@]     @ @@@@                    UNTIL I=4 @F@@@@                    LET XS
)@@G@@A=VALUE(<A$CODE>) @ EVALUATE AREA CODE    @G@@@@                    ERROXT
)@@G@@R DUNARE @ SKIP IT IF NOT IN SCHEMA ANYMORE     @D@@@@                  XU
)@@G@@  AREA,PN (A) @ GET THAT AREA'S INFO@ @@@@                    ERROR     XV
)@@G@@@H@@@@                    LET [ABITS:ASEQ,1] = 1 @ SET BIT SHOWING THIS XW
)@@G@@AREA SAVED  @^@@@@                    @   @F@@@@                    REPEXX
)@@G@@AT I=1,1 @ LOAD # PRIME PGS INTO <P$RIME> @E@@@@                      LEXY
)@@G@@T [P$RIME:I,6] = [IOBUF:23+I,6]     @ @@@@                    UNTIL I=6 XZ
)@@G@@@F@@@@                    LET P=VALUE(<P$RIME>) @ EVALUATE PRIME PGS    YA
)@@G@@@^@@@@                    @   @F@@@@                    IF IOBUF[5]:S1<>YB
)@@G@@'*' THEN @ OVERFLOW EXISTS    @G@@@@                      REPEAT I=1,1 @YC
)@@G@@ LOAD # OVERFLOW PGS INTO <O$FLOW>  @E@@@@                        LET [OYD
)@@G@@$FLOW:I,6] = [IOBUF:30+I,6]   @A@@@@                      UNTIL I=9     YE
)@@G@@@G@@@@                      LET O=VALUE(<O$FLOW>) @ EVALUATE OVERFLOW PGYF
)@@G@@S     @C@@@@                    ELSE @ NO OVERFLOW EXISTS   @ @@@@      YG
)@@G@@                LET O=0 @ @@@@                    END IF    @^@@@@      YH
)@@G@@              @   @H@@@@                    LET DATA(CYCX,ASEQ):H1=P @ SYI
)@@G@@AVE # PRIME FOR THIS AREA     @F@@@@                    LET DATA(CYCX,ASYJ
)@@G@@EQ):H2=O @    & # OFLOW TOO   @^@@@@DUNARE:             @   @^@@@@      YK
)@@G@@            END IF@^@@@@                END IF  @^@@@@              END YL
)@@G@@IF    @#@@@@            END DO@#@@@@RDDONE:     @     @B@@@@            YM
)@@G@@IF OPTS:Z WRITE CLOSE <FILE>  @^@@@@            CLOSE $$SR$$@#@@@@      YN
)@@G@@    END IF  @ @@@@        UNTIL CYC#=MAXCYCLES  @]@@@@        @   @E@@@@YO
)@@G@@        IF CYCX=0 WRITE,S = '<SRDUMP> NO DATA AVAILABLE.',* @]@@@@      YP
)@@G@@  @   @ @@@@        WRITE TITLE <FDT:1,2> @F@@@@        WRITE DATIM DATEYQ
)@@G@@:NT1,DATE:NT2,DATE:NT3,TIME:NT1,TIME:NT2  @]@@@@        @   @A@@@@      YR
)@@G@@  @ NOW PRODUCE THE HEADINGS  @]@@@@        @   @B@@@@        WRITE = ' YS
)@@G@@        ',C15,'AREA',C21@D@@@@        REPEAT I=1,1 @ LOOP THRU ALL VALIDYT
)@@G@@ FILE CYCLES@ @@@@          WRITE TDFORM TD(I,1)@A@@@@          WRITE = YU
)@@G@@X1,'      ',X1    @^@@@@        UNTIL I=CYCX    @#@@@@        WRITE *   YV
)@@G@@@]@@@@        @   @B@@@@        WRITE = 'AREA NAME',C15,'CODE',C21@D@@@@YW
)@@G@@        REPEAT I=1,1 @ LOOP THRU ALL VALID FILE CYCLES@ @@@@          WRYX
)@@G@@ITE TDFORM TD(I,2)@B@@@@          IF I<CYCX WRITE = X1,'GROWTH',X1@^@@@@YY
)@@G@@        UNTIL I=CYCX    @#@@@@        WRITE *   @]@@@@        @   @C@@@@YZ
)@@G@@        WRITE = '============',C15,'====',C21   @D@@@@        REPEAT I=1ZA
)@@G@@,1 @ LOOP THRU ALL VALID FILE CYCLES@ @@@@          WRITE = '====='     ZB
)@@G@@@B@@@@          IF I<CYCX WRITE = X1,'======',X1@^@@@@        UNTIL I=CYZC
)@@G@@CX    @#@@@@        WRITE *   @]@@@@        @   @A@@@@        @ NOW PRODZD
)@@G@@UCE THE REPORT    @]@@@@        @   @C@@@@        REPEAT AREA#=1,1 @ LOOZE
)@@G@@P THRU ALL AREAS  @E@@@@          IF [ABITS:AREA#,1]=1 THEN @ THIS AREA ZF
)@@G@@INCLUDED    @ @@@@            AREA,PN #AREA#    @B@@@@            WRITE ZG
)@@G@@AINFO <ART:4,5>,ACODE   @ @@@@            REPEAT CYC#=1,1   @E@@@@      ZH
)@@G@@        LET THIS = DATA(CYC#,AREA#):H1 @ PRIME PAGES  @A@@@@            ZI
)@@G@@  WRITE VALUES THIS     @ @@@@VALUES:       FORMAT D5,X2    @D@@@@      ZJ
)@@G@@        IF CYC#<CYCX THEN @ DON'T DO FINAL CYCLE@G@@@@                LEZK
)@@G@@T NEXT = DATA(CYC#+1,AREA#):H1 @ NEXT CYCLE'S DATA    @D@@@@            ZL
)@@G@@    LET GROWTH = (NEXT - THIS) % THIS     @B@@@@                IF GROWTZM
)@@G@@H<>0 THEN @ SHOW %@B@@@@                  WRITE GROWTH GROWTH     @A@@@@ZN
)@@G@@GROWTH:           FORMAT D3,'%  '   @A@@@@                ELSE @ 0% GROWZO
)@@G@@TH    @ @@@@                  WRITE = X6  @^@@@@                END IF  ZP
)@@G@@@^@@@@              END IF    @ @@@@            UNTIL CYC#=CYCX   @^@@@@ZQ
)@@G@@            WRITE *     @#@@@@          END IF  @A@@@@        UNTIL AREAZR
)@@G@@#=SCRT[010]:H1    @#@@@@        RETURN    @]@@@@        @   @^@@@@OPNERRZS
)@@G@@: @ ERROR ON OPEN @^@@@@        LET OPNERR=1    @ @@@@        GO TO OPNRZT
)@@G@@ET @ RETURN _@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@ZU
)@@G@@*[S@@[*SDFF*@A@@@@G1-GS'^[&H92H(-I))G06 -8AC?H81AK? K)@C@@@@^[?G(4^[8B(<ZV
)@@G@@IT& @$C[&IL>G*)G-+G*%IT2IT-I1> 0$ C)@C@@@@^[(G0)J@/B00^[7IL(I->^[&GD<^@$ZW
)@@G@@G12G(>AC'^8?J@)^@)@D@@@@^[?G(4^[8B(<IT& @$C[<GD4 -0^[=GL> L3IL3GD6G** S1ZX
)@@G@@ C,^8(@C@@@@^[(G0)J@/B00^[7IL(I->^[&GD<^@$GT-I)'^@)^8?J@)^@)@C@@@@^[?G(4ZY
)@@G@@^[8B(<IT& @$C[-IT$ --^[=GL> L3IL3GD6G*,^8(@C@@@@^[(G0)J@/B00^[7IL(I->^[&ZZ
)@@G@@GD<^@$GD3G8'^@)^8?J@)^@)@E@@@@^[?G(4^[8B(<IT& @$C[5IT>^@=^-NEK=^), -=GL>AA
)@@G@@ L3IL3GD6G*,^8(^@)@C@@@@^[(G0)J@/B00^[7IL(I->^[&GD<^@$I(3G*'^@)^8?J@)^@)AB
)@@G@@@D@@@@^[?G(4^[8B(<IT& @$C[+IL:I[4^[0IL(H14^)\^)=ETM^)=^8(^@)@C@@@@^[(G0)AC
)@@G@@J@/B00^[7IL(I->^[&GD<^@$GL2HT0AC'^8?J@)^@)@^@@@@^[3HD'G*!IL>I[\IL4^@%GC%AD
)@@G@@@B@@@@^[?G(4^[8B(<IT& @$C[+IL:I[4^[0IL(H14^)$ C)@C@@@@^[(G0)J@/B00^[7IL(AE
)@@G@@I->^[&GD<^@$GL2HT0AK'^8?J@)^@)@C@@@@^[?G(4^[8B(<IT& @$C[&IL>G*)G-+G*%IT2AF

)@@G@@: FORMAT WF,' FILENAME: "',<6>WF,'"',*,*  @A@@@@VFORM:  FORMAT C5,'"',<2CZ
)@@G@@>F6,'"',*   @ @@@@OFORM:  FORMAT C5,'"',F6,'"',*@A@@@@SCFORM: FORMAT *,'DA
)@@G@@SCHEMA: ',<2>WF,* @A@@@@LVFORM: FORMAT *,'DMS LEVEL = ',D,* @H@@@@SSNFE:DB
)@@G@@  FORMAT 'SUBSCHEMA ',<2>WF,' CANNOT BE LOCATED IN FILE ',<2>WF,'.',*   DC
)@@G@@@H@@@@SSNFT:  FORMAT 'SUBSCHEMA ',<2>WF,' CANNOT BE LOCATED IN TIP FILE DD
)@@G@@',WF,'.',*  @^@@@@PCALL1: FORMAT '@',WF,D @^@@@@PCALL2: FORMAT ',',<2>WFDE
)@@G@@@^@@@@PCALL3: FORMAT <10>WF   @ @@@@PCALL4: FORMAT ',',<10>WF     @H@@@@DF
)@@G@@SIFORM: FORMAT 'CANNOT READ INPUT FILE "',<10>WF,'".  DMS LEVEL 8 ASSUMEDG
)@@G@@D.',* @G@@@@PROCAL: FORMAT WF,'/ETC 1R1.7  ',F2,'/',F2,'/',F2,X2,F2,':',DH
)@@G@@F2,':',F2,* @ @@@@NA4:    FORMAT  <NWORDS>A4    @]@@@@        @   @G@@@@DI
)@@G@@        IF OPTS:H WRITE,S = 'ETC PROCESSOR,DMR,OPTION-MAP,SI,RO,SO',*   DJ
)@@G@@@]@@@@        @   @H@@@@        LET CSF = CSF('@ASG,I $$SL$$.') @ FREE SDK
)@@G@@CHEMA LIST FILE WHEN DONE     @G@@@@        LET CSF = CSF('@ASG,I CSINTNDL
)@@G@@AME$.') @ FREE DBE FILE WHEN DONE   @]@@@@        @   @D@@@@        DIM DM
)@@G@@PRCSR(1),DMR(1),SI$(10),RO$(10),SO$(10)   @]@@@@        @   @F@@@@      DN
)@@G@@  PARAMETER <PRCSR>,<DMR>,OPTMAP,<SI$>:0,<RO$>:0,<SO$>:0    @C@@@@      DO
)@@G@@  LET LANG = PRCSR(1) @ PROGRAM LANGUAGE  @E@@@@        LET DEBUG? = OPTDP
)@@G@@S:Z @ OR OPTMAP:Z @ DEBUG OPTION    @]@@@@        @   @I@@@@        WRITDQ
)@@G@@E PROCAL LANG,DATE:NT1,DATE:NT2,DATE:NT3,TIME:NT1,TIME:NT2,TIME:NT3     DR
)@@G@@@]@@@@        @   @D@@@@        LET READ$ = (SI$(1)=0) @ TRUE IF NO "SI"DS
)@@G@@ FIELD@C@@@@        IF READ$ THEN @ READING FROM READ$ FILE @B@@@@      DT
)@@G@@    LET CSF = CSF('@ASG,T $$ETC2$.')@E@@@@          IF CSF<0 WRITE,S = 'DU
)@@G@@"ETC" INTERNAL ERROR 4.',*    @A@@@@          OPEN SDFO $$ETC2$=$$ETC2$.DV
)@@G@@@B@@@@        ELSE @ READING FROM "SI" FILE     @B@@@@          ERROR SIDW
)@@G@@NFG @ IN CASE OF ERROR  @A@@@@          OPEN SDFI $$ETC3$=<SI$>   @#@@@@DX
)@@G@@          ERROR   @#@@@@        END IF    @]@@@@        @   @F@@@@      DY
)@@G@@  DIM KWFLAGS(12), KWTABLE(12), DATA(15), PCT(3), INBUF(33) @G@@@@      DZ
)@@G@@  DIM VARIABLE(10,2), OPTIONAL(10), FILENAME(6), SS(2), SCH(2)    @]@@@@EA
)@@G@@        @   @C@@@@        LET RKEYWORD = 'K' @ REQUIRED KEYWORD   @C@@@@EB
)@@G@@        LET OKEYWORD = 'O' @ OPTIONAL KEYWORD   @C@@@@        LET RVARIAEC
)@@G@@BLE = 'V' @ REQUIRED VARIABLE @G@@@@        LET LVARIABLE = 'L' @ REQUIRED
)@@G@@ED VARIABLE: LONGER THAN 2 WORDS    @]@@@@        @   @ @@@@        IF LEE
)@@G@@ANG='QLP   ' THEN @ @@@@          LET KWFLAGS(1) = 'K'@A@@@@          LEEF
)@@G@@T KWTABLE(1) = 'INVOKE' @E@@@@          LET KWFLAGS(2) = 'V'          @ EG
)@@G@@SUBSCHEMA NAME    @ @@@@          LET KWTABLE(2) = '' @ @@@@          LEEH
)@@G@@T KWFLAGS(3) = 'O'@A@@@@          LET KWTABLE(3) = 'IN    ' @ @@@@      EI
)@@G@@    LET KWFLAGS(4) = 'O'@A@@@@          LET KWTABLE(4) = 'OF    ' @ @@@@EJ
)@@G@@          LET KWFLAGS(5) = 'O'@A@@@@          LET KWTABLE(5) = 'TIP   ' EK
)@@G@@@ @@@@          LET KWFLAGS(6) = 'O'@A@@@@          LET KWTABLE(6) = 'FIEL
)@@G@@LE  ' @E@@@@          LET KWFLAGS(7) = 'L'          @ FILE NAME / NUMBEREM
)@@G@@@ @@@@          LET KWTABLE(7) = '' @]@@@@          @ @^@@@@          LEEN
)@@G@@T NUMKW=7   @D@@@@        ELSE IF LANG='DMU   ' OR LANG='ADMLP ' THEN   EO
)@@G@@@ @@@@          LET KWFLAGS(1) = 'K'@A@@@@          LET KWTABLE(1) = 'INEP
)@@G@@VOKE' @ @@@@          LET KWFLAGS(2) = 'K'@A@@@@          LET KWTABLE(2)EQ
)@@G@@ = 'SUBSCH' @E@@@@          LET KWFLAGS(3) = 'V'          @ SUBSCHEMA NAER
)@@G@@ME    @ @@@@          LET KWTABLE(3) = '' @ @@@@          LET KWFLAGS(4)ES
)@@G@@ = 'O'@A@@@@          LET KWTABLE(4) = 'IN    ' @ @@@@          LET KWFLET
)@@G@@AGS(5) = 'O'@A@@@@          LET KWTABLE(5) = 'TIP   ' @ @@@@          LEEU
)@@G@@T KWFLAGS(6) = 'O'@A@@@@          LET KWTABLE(6) = 'FILE  ' @E@@@@      EV
)@@G@@    LET KWFLAGS(7) = 'L'          @ FILE NAME / NUMBER@ @@@@          LEEW
)@@G@@T KWTABLE(7) = '' @ @@@@          LET KWFLAGS(8) = 'O'@A@@@@          LEEX
)@@G@@T KWTABLE(8) = 'OF    ' @ @@@@          LET KWFLAGS(9) = 'K'@A@@@@      EY
)@@G@@    LET KWTABLE(9) = 'SCHEMA' @D@@@@          LET KWFLAGS(10) = 'V'     EZ
)@@G@@   @ SCHEMA NAME  @ @@@@          LET KWTABLE(10) = ''@]@@@@          @ FA
)@@G@@@^@@@@          LET NUMKW=10  @A@@@@        ELSE IF LANG='SDDL  ' THEN  FB
)@@G@@@ @@@@          LET KWFLAGS(1) = 'K'@A@@@@          LET KWTABLE(1) = 'SUFC
)@@G@@BSCH' @ @@@@          LET KWFLAGS(2) = 'O'@A@@@@          LET KWTABLE(2)FD
)@@G@@ = 'NAME  ' @ @@@@          LET KWFLAGS(3) = 'O'@A@@@@          LET KWTAFE
)@@G@@BLE(3) = 'IS    ' @E@@@@          LET KWFLAGS(4) = 'V'          @ SUBSCHFF
)@@G@@EMA NAME    @ @@@@          LET KWTABLE(4) = '' @ @@@@          LET KWFLFG
)@@G@@AGS(5) = 'O'@A@@@@          LET KWTABLE(5) = 'IN    ' @ @@@@          LEFH
)@@G@@T KWFLAGS(6) = 'O'@A@@@@          LET KWTABLE(6) = 'TIP   ' @ @@@@      FI
)@@G@@    LET KWFLAGS(7) = 'O'@A@@@@          LET KWTABLE(7) = 'FILE  ' @E@@@@FJ
)@@G@@          LET KWFLAGS(8) = 'L'          @ FILE NAME / NUMBER@ @@@@      FK
)@@G@@    LET KWTABLE(8) = '' @ @@@@          LET KWFLAGS(9) = 'O'@A@@@@      FL
)@@G@@    LET KWTABLE(9) = 'OF    ' @A@@@@          LET KWFLAGS(10) = 'K'     FM
)@@G@@@A@@@@          LET KWTABLE(10) = 'SCHEMA'@D@@@@          LET KWFLAGS(11FN
)@@G@@) = 'V'        @ SCHEMA NAME  @ @@@@          LET KWTABLE(11) = ''@]@@@@FO
)@@G@@          @ @^@@@@          LET NUMKW=11  @]@@@@        ELSE@E@@@@      FP
)@@G@@    WRITE,S = 'UNKNOWN SUBSCHEMA LANGUAGE TYPE.',*    @#@@@@        END FQ
)@@G@@IF    @]@@@@        @   @F@@@@        @ READ INPUT LINE-BY-LINE, UNTIL AFR
)@@G@@ SCHEMA NAME IS FOUND   @]@@@@        @   @^@@@@        LET KW^ = 1     FS
)@@G@@@#@@@@        LET O^ = 1@#@@@@        LET V^ = 1@^@@@@        LET DONE =FT
)@@G@@ 0    @]@@@@        @   @B@@@@        REPEAT @ LOOP THRU LINES OF DATA  FU
)@@G@@@]@@@@          @ @A@@@@          @ READ A LINE OF DATA     @]@@@@      FV
)@@G@@    @ @D@@@@          IF READ$ THEN @ READING FROM READ$ FILE     @A@@@@FW
)@@G@@            ERROR EOF @ JUST IN CASE@C@@@@            TREAD '',<INBUF> @FX
)@@G@@ READ AN IMAGE    @#@@@@            ERROR @F@@@@            PUT $$ETC2$ FY
)@@G@@<INBUF:1,NWORDS> @ WRITE IMAGE TO SAVEFILE@A@@@@            LET CHARSREAFZ
)@@G@@D = 6*NWORDS@B@@@@          ELSE @ READING FROM "SI" FILE   @E@@@@      GA
)@@G@@      GET $$ETC3$ (EOF=EOF) <INBUF> @ READ AN IMAGE   @C@@@@            GB
)@@G@@IF CHRSET = 1 THEN @ ASCII IMAGE    @B@@@@              LET CHARSREAD = GC
)@@G@@4 * NWORDS  @A@@@@              IF NWORDS > 0 THEN    @G@@@@            GD
)@@G@@    WRITE NA4 <INBUF:1,NWORDS> @ PUT IT IN FIELDATA IN WBUF @E@@@@      GE
)@@G@@          LET <INBUF> = <WBUF> @ THEN COPY IT BACK    @C@@@@            GF
)@@G@@    WRITE = R @ CLEAR WRITE BUFFER  @^@@@@              END IF    @B@@@@GG
)@@G@@            ELSE @ FIELDATA IMAGE READ    @B@@@@              LET CHARSRGH
)@@G@@EAD = 6*NWORDS    @#@@@@            END IF@#@@@@          END IF  @A@@@@GI
)@@G@@          IF LANG='ADMLP ' THEN     @F@@@@            IF CHARSREAD>72 LEGJ
)@@G@@T CHARSREAD=72 @ IGNORE COMMENTS    @D@@@@            LET INBUF(1)='    GK
)@@G@@  ' @ CLEAR COLS 1-6    @#@@@@          END IF  @^@@@@          IF DEBUGGL
)@@G@@? THEN@A@@@@            WRITE = *,'LINE READ:',*@^@@@@            P!,F IGM
)@@G@@NBUF  @#@@@@          END IF  @]@@@@          @ @^@@@@          LET IN^ GN
)@@G@@= 1   @D@@@@          LET CONTIN? = 0 @ MARK AS NOT CONTINUED     @C@@@@GO
)@@G@@          REPEAT @ LOOP THRU WORDS ON A LINE    @G@@@@            WHILE GP
)@@G@@IN^ <= CHARSREAD AND [INBUF:IN^,6] = ' ' @ SPAN SPACES@A@@@@            GQ
)@@G@@  LET IN^ = IN^ + 1     @^@@@@            END WHILE   @#@@@@            GR
)@@G@@@     @#@@@@            @     @H@@@@            IF IN^>CHARSREAD OR [INBGS
)@@G@@UF:IN^,6]=';' OR [INBUF:IN^,6]='.' THEN   @D@@@@              LET CONTINGT
)@@G@@? = 1 @ FLAG AS CONTINUED     @H@@@@            ELSE IF LANG='QLP   ' ANGU
)@@G@@D [INBUF:1,6]='*' THEN @ QLP: "*" IN COL 1@ @@@@              LET CONTINGV
)@@G@@?=1   @I@@@@            ELSE IF LANG='ADMLP ' AND [INBUF:7,6]='*' THEN @GW
)@@G@@ ADMLP: "*" IN COL 7    @ @@@@              LET CONTIN?=1   @I@@@@      GX
)@@G@@      ELSE IF LANG='ADMLP ' AND [INBUF:7,6]='/' THEN @ ADMLP: "/" IN COLGY
)@@G@@ 7    @ @@@@              LET CONTIN?=1   @#@@@@            ELSE  @D@@@@GZ
)@@G@@              LET PCT(1) = IN^ @ CHAR # TO START WITH @C@@@@            HA
)@@G@@  LET MAXCHARS = CHARSREAD - IN^ + 1@D@@@@              @ IF MAXCHARS > HB
)@@G@@12 LET MAXCHARS = 12    @I@@@@              LET <DATA>=BREAK <INBUF>,'  HC
)@@G@@  ;.',MAXCHARS,<PCT> @ GET REST OF WORD   @F@@@@              IF PCT(3)<HD
)@@G@@7 LET DATA(2) = '      ' @ CLEAR 2ND WORD @ @@@@              IF DEBUG? HE
)@@G@@THEN  @B@@@@                WRITE = *,'WORD READ:',*  @ @@@@            HF
)@@G@@    P!,F DATA     @^@@@@              END IF    @E@@@@              LET HG
)@@G@@IN^ = IN^ + PCT(3) @ MOVE INPUT POINTER   @H@@@@              IF PCT(2)=HH
)@@G@@';' OR PCT(2)='.' OR IN^ > CHARSREAD LET CONTIN? = 1  @#@@@@            HI
)@@G@@  @   @ @@@@              LET LOOP? = 1   @ @@@@              WHILE LOOPHJ
)@@G@@?     @H@@@@                IF KWFLAGS(KW^) = OKEYWORD THEN @ EXPECTING HK
)@@G@@OPTIONAL KEYWORD  @F@@@@                  IF DEBUG? WRITE = 'EXPECTING OHL
)@@G@@PTIONAL KEYWORD',*@F@@@@                  IF DATA(1) = KWTABLE(KW^) THENHM
)@@G@@ @ FOUND A MATCH  @F@@@@                    IF DEBUG? WRITE = 'MATCHED OHN
)@@G@@PTIONAL KEYWORD',*@G@@@@                    LET OPTIONAL(O^) = DATA(1) @HO
)@@G@@ SAVE OPTIONAL DATA     @E@@@@                    LET O^ = O^ + 1 @ PREPHP
)@@G@@ARE FOR NEXT TIME @D@@@@                    LET LOOP? = 0 @ END THIS LOOHQ
)@@G@@P     @H@@@@                    LET KEEPLOOKING? = 0 @ WE ALREADY KNOW WHR
)@@G@@HAT KIND IT IS    @B@@@@                  ELSE @ NOT THIS ONE     @G@@@@HS
)@@G@@                    IF DEBUG? WRITE = 'NO MATCH ON OPTIONAL KEYWORD',*  HT
)@@G@@@E@@@@                    LET KW^ = KW^ + 1, 1 @ TRY NEXT ONE     @D@@@@HU
)@@G@@                    IF KW^ > NUMKW THEN @ HIT THE END?@D@@@@            HV
)@@G@@          LET LOOP? = 0 @ STOP THIS LOOP  @F@@@@                      LEHW
)@@G@@T KEEPLOOKING? = 0 @ DON'T KEEP SEARCHING @D@@@@                      LEHX
)@@G@@T KW^ = 1 @ START OVER AGAIN  @A@@@@                      LET V^ = 1    HY
)@@G@@@A@@@@                      LET O^ = 1    @ @@@@                    END HZ
)@@G@@IF    @^@@@@                  END IF@E@@@@                ELSE @ NOT EXPIA
)@@G@@ECTING AN OPTIONAL KEYWORD    @C@@@@                  LET LOOP? = 0 @ GEIB
)@@G@@T OUT NOW   @E@@@@                  LET KEEPLOOKING? = 1 @ AND CONTINUE IC
)@@G@@SCAN  @^@@@@                END IF  @^@@@@              END WHILE @#@@@@ID
)@@G@@              @   @A@@@@              IF KEEPLOOKING? THEN @@G@@@@      IE
)@@G@@          IF KWFLAGS(KW^) = RKEYWORD THEN @ LOOKING FOR A KEYWORD @F@@@@IF
)@@G@@                  IF DEBUG? WRITE = 'EXPECTING REQUIRED KEYWORD',*@F@@@@IG
)@@G@@                  IF DATA(1) = KWTABLE(KW^) THEN @ FOUND A KEYWORD@G@@@@IH
)@@G@@                    IF DEBUG? WRITE = 'MATCH ON REQUIRED KEYWORD',*     II
)@@G@@@G@@@@                    LET KW^ = KW^ +1 @ POINT TO NEXT KEYWORD TABLEIJ
)@@G@@ ENTRY@C@@@@                  ELSE @ NOT WHAT WE EXPECTED   @I@@@@      IK
)@@G@@              IF DEBUG? WRITE = 'NO MATCH ON REQUIRED KEYWORD. START AGAIL
)@@G@@IN.',*@D@@@@                    LET KW^ = 1 @ START OVER AGAIN    @ @@@@IM
)@@G@@                    LET V^ = 1@ @@@@                    LET O^ = 1@^@@@@IN
)@@G@@                  END IF@C@@@@                ELSE @ LOOKING FOR VARIABLIO
)@@G@@E     @I@@@@                  IF DEBUG? WRITE = 'EXPECTING VARIABLE. WILIP
)@@G@@L KEEP THIS ONE.',*     @G@@@@                  LET VARIABLE(V^,1) = DATIQ
)@@G@@A(1) @ SAVE VARIABLE DATA     @C@@@@                  LET VARIABLE(V^,2)IR
)@@G@@ = DATA(2)  @H@@@@                  IF KWFLAGS(KW^)='L' LET <FILENAME>=<IS
)@@G@@DATA> @ LONG VARIABLE   @E@@@@                  LET V^ = V^ + 1 @ PREPARIT
)@@G@@E FOR NEXT TIME   @F@@@@                  LET KW^ = KW^ + 1 @ NEXT ENTRYIU
)@@G@@ IN KEYWORD TABLE @^@@@@                END IF  @^@@@@              END IV
)@@G@@IF    @#@@@@              @   @B@@@@              IF KW^ > NUMKW LET DONIW
)@@G@@E = 1 @#@@@@            END IF@#@@@@            @     @B@@@@          UNIX
)@@G@@TIL CONTIN? = 1 OR DONE = 1   @]@@@@          @ @^@@@@        UNTIL DONEIY
)@@G@@ = 1  @C@@@@        IF DEBUG? WRITE = 'END OF PARSING.',*   @]@@@@      IZ
)@@G@@  @   @B@@@@        LET TIP?=0 @ ASSUME EXEC-8 FILE   @F@@@@        IF OJA
)@@G@@^>1 THEN @ CAN ONLY BE TIP IF OPTIONALS INCLUDE 'TIP' @C@@@@          REJB
)@@G@@PEAT I=1,1 @ LOOP THRU ALL OPTIONALS@C@@@@            IF OPTIONAL(I)='TIJC
)@@G@@P   ' LET TIP?=1  @ @@@@          UNTIL I=O^ OR TIP?=1@#@@@@        END JD
)@@G@@IF    @]@@@@        @   @ @@@@        IF DEBUG? THEN @ DEBUG@F@@@@      JE
)@@G@@    WRITE FNFORM (TIP?=0)*'EXEC'+(TIP?*'TIP'),<FILENAME>    @A@@@@      JF
)@@G@@    WRITE = 'VARIABLES: ',*   @^@@@@          REPEAT I=1,1  @D@@@@      JG
)@@G@@      WRITE VFORM VARIABLE(I,1),VARIABLE(I,2)   @^@@@@          UNTIL I=JH
)@@G@@V^-1  @A@@@@          WRITE = *,'OPTIONALS: ',* @^@@@@          IF O^>1 JI
)@@G@@THEN  @^@@@@            REPEAT I=1,1@B@@@@              WRITE OFORM OPTIJJ
)@@G@@ONAL(I)     @^@@@@            UNTIL I=O^-1@#@@@@          END IF  @#@@@@JK
)@@G@@        END IF    @]@@@@        @   @F@@@@        @ QLP SYNTAX DOES NOT JL
)@@G@@SPECIFY A SCHEMA NAME, SO WE MUST   @F@@@@        @ READ THE SUBSCHEMA SJM
)@@G@@PECIFIED FROM ITS FILE TO FIND TO   @A@@@@        @ WHICH SCHEMA IT BELOJN
)@@G@@NGS.  @]@@@@        @   @F@@@@        IF LANG='QLP   ' THEN @ MUST READ JO
)@@G@@SS TO FIND SCHEMA IF QLP@F@@@@          LET SS(1)=VARIABLE(1,1)       @ JP
)@@G@@SAVE SUBSCHEMA NAME     @A@@@@          LET SS(2)=VARIABLE(1,2)   @E@@@@JQ
)@@G@@          LET FILENAME(1)=VARIABLE(2,1) @ AND FILE NAME     @B@@@@      JR
)@@G@@    LET FILENAME(2)=VARIABLE(2,2)   @E@@@@          LET TOC^ = -1 @ JUSTJS
)@@G@@ IN CASE WE FAIL FILE READ    @C@@@@          ERROR FILENG @ PREPARE FORJT
)@@G@@ I/O ERROR  @A@@@@          IF TIP?=0 THEN @ EXEC FILE@E@@@@            JU
)@@G@@LET TS = TOCSIZE <FILENAME> @ FIND SIZE OF TOC  @^@@@@            DIM TOJV
)@@G@@C(TS) @D@@@@            LET <TOC> = GETTOC <FILENAME> @ READ TOC  @ @@@@JW
)@@G@@          ELSE @ TIP FILE     @E@@@@            LET TS = TOCSIZE,T <FILEJX
)@@G@@NAME> @ FIND SIZE OF TOC@^@@@@            DIM TOC(TS) @D@@@@            JY
)@@G@@LET <TOC> = GETTOC,T <FILENAME> @ READ TOC@#@@@@          END IF  @G@@@@JZ
)@@G@@          LET TOC^ = PFS,A <TOC>,<SS>     @ LOCATE SUBSCHEMA IN TOC     KA
)@@G@@@#@@@@FILENG:   ERROR   @B@@@@          IF TOC^ < 0 THEN @ NOT FOUND    KB
)@@G@@@ @@@@            IF TIP?=0 THEN    @B@@@@              WRITE SSNFE <SS>KC
)@@G@@,<FILENAME> @#@@@@            ELSE  @B@@@@              WRITE SSNFT <SS>KD
)@@G@@,FILENAME(1)@#@@@@            END IF@F@@@@            STOP @ END IT ALL KE
)@@G@@HERE IF WE CAN'T LOCATE SUBSCHEMA!  @#@@@@          END IF  @]@@@@      KF
)@@G@@    @ @^@@@@          IF TIP? THEN  @B@@@@            OPEN DISC,T SCHFILKG
)@@G@@=<FILENAME> @#@@@@          ELSE    @B@@@@            OPEN DISC SCHFIL=<KH
)@@G@@FILENAME>   @#@@@@          END IF  @F@@@@          GET SCHFIL(BLOCK=TOCKI
)@@G@@(TOC^+010),NWORDS=28) @ READ SFD    @^@@@@          CLOSE SCHFIL  @E@@@@KJ
)@@G@@          LET <SCH> = <IOBUF: 011,012> @ SAVE SCHEMA NAME   @ @@@@      KK
)@@G@@  ELSE @ OTHER THAN QLP @A@@@@          LET SCH(1) = VARIABLE(3,1)@A@@@@KL
)@@G@@          LET SCH(2) = VARIABLE(3,2)@#@@@@        END IF    @G@@@@      KM
)@@G@@  IF LANG='QLP   ' AND SCH(1)=0 THEN @ MUST BE ADP APPLICATION    @A@@@@KN
)@@G@@          LET LEV=8 @ ASSUME LEVEL 8@D@@@@          GOTO BLDADD @ DON'T KO
)@@G@@BOTHER WITH SCHEMA LIST @#@@@@        END IF    @A@@@@        IF DEBUG? KP
)@@G@@WRITE SCFORM <SCH>@]@@@@        @   @ @@@@        @ READ SCHEMA LIST    KQ
)@@G@@@]@@@@        @   @A@@@@        ERROR SLNFG @ JUST IN CASE  @A@@@@      KR
)@@G@@  OPEN DISC $$SL$$=$$SL$$     @G@@@@        GET $$SL$$ (BLOCK=0, NWORDS=KS
)@@G@@1)          @ READ # SCHEMAS IN LIST@F@@@@        GET $$SL$$ (BLOCK=1, NKT
)@@G@@WORDS=IOBUF[0]*2) @ READ SCHEMA LIST@^@@@@        CLOSE $$SL$$    @#@@@@KU
)@@G@@        ERROR     @B@@@@        LET CSF = CSF ('@FREE $$SL$$')    @]@@@@KV
)@@G@@        @   @E@@@@        @ SEARCH FOR SCHEMA NAME IN SCHEMA LIST (IN IOKW
)@@G@@BUF)  @]@@@@        @   @^@@@@        LET DONE = 0    @^@@@@        LET KX
)@@G@@IO^ = 0     @^@@@@        WHILE DONE=0    @H@@@@          LET IO^ = SEARKY
)@@G@@CH ( <IOBUF>, SCH(1), IO^, 2) @ FIND 1ST WD OF SCHEMA @B@@@@          IFKZ
)@@G@@ IO^ < 0 THEN @ NOT IN LIST   @^@@@@            LET DONE = 1@A@@@@      LA
)@@G@@    ELSE @ MATCH ON 1ST WORD  @F@@@@            IF IOBUF[IO^+1] = SCH(2)LB
)@@G@@ THEN @ MATCH ON 2ND WORD TOO @ @@@@              LET DONE = 1    @B@@@@LC
)@@G@@            ELSE @ 2ND WORD DOESN'T MATCH @D@@@@              LET IO^ = LD
)@@G@@IO^ + 2 @ POINT TO NEXT ENTRY @#@@@@            END IF@#@@@@          ENLE
)@@G@@D IF  @#@@@@        END WHILE @]@@@@        @   @B@@@@        IF IO^ < 0LF
)@@G@@ THEN @ NOT IN LIST     @B@@@@          LET LEV = 10 @ MUST BE LEVEL 10 LG
)@@G@@@A@@@@        ELSE @ FOUND IN SCHEMA LIST @B@@@@          LET LEV = 8 @ LH
)@@G@@MUST BE LEVEL 8   @#@@@@        END IF    @A@@@@BLDADD: IF DEBUG? WRITE LI
)@@G@@LVFORM LEV  @A@@@@        IF DMR(1) = 'PDMS  ' THEN   @^@@@@          LELJ
)@@G@@T AP = 1    @B@@@@        ELSE IF DMR(1) = 'TDMS  ' THEN    @^@@@@      LK
)@@G@@    LET AP = 2    @B@@@@        ELSE IF DMR(1) = 'VDMS  ' THEN    @^@@@@LL
)@@G@@          LET AP = 3    @]@@@@        ELSE@C@@@@          WRITE,S = '"ETLM
)@@G@@C" INTERNAL ERROR 2.',* @#@@@@        END IF    @A@@@@        IF LEV=10 LN
)@@G@@LET AP = AP + 3   @]@@@@        @   @E@@@@        @ BUILD ADD-STREAM CALLO
)@@G@@LING THE APPROPRIATE PROCESSOR@]@@@@        @   @B@@@@        LET CSF = LP
)@@G@@CSF('@ASG,T $$ETC1$.')  @D@@@@        IF CSF<0 WRITE,S = '"ETC" INTERNALLQ
)@@G@@ ERROR 1.',*@A@@@@        OPEN SDFO $$ETC1$=$$ETC1$.  @]@@@@        @   LR
)@@G@@@A@@@@        WRITE PCALL1 <PRCSR>,AP     @G@@@@        OPTBIT2ALPHA,WL LS
)@@G@@OPTMAP @ ADD COMMA AND OPTIONS IF NECESSARY     @^@@@@        WRITE = ' LT
)@@G@@'     @B@@@@        IF SI$(1)<>0 WRITE PCALL3 <SI$>   @B@@@@        IF RLU
)@@G@@O$(1)<>0 WRITE PCALL4 <RO$>   @B@@@@        IF SO$(1)<>0 WRITE PCALL4 <SLV
)@@G@@O$>   @H@@@@        PUT $$ETC1$ *                                @ PROCELW
)@@G@@SSOR CALL LINE    @ @@@@        IF DEBUG? WRITE *     @#@@@@        WRITLX
)@@G@@E = R @]@@@@        @   @^@@@@        IF READ$ THEN   @D@@@@          CLLY
)@@G@@OSE $$ETC2$ @ CLOSE INPUT IMAGE SAVEFILE  @A@@@@          WRITE = '@ADD LZ
)@@G@@$$ETC2$.'   @G@@@@          PUT $$ETC1$ *                              @MA
)@@G@@ "@ADD INVOKE ..."@ @@@@          IF DEBUG? WRITE *   @^@@@@          WRMB
)@@G@@ITE = R     @#@@@@        END IF    @]@@@@        @   @B@@@@CLOSE1: CLOSMC
)@@G@@E $$ETC1$ @ CLOSE @ADD FILE   @]@@@@        @   @A@@@@        @ ADD THE MD
)@@G@@FILE "$$ETC1$"    @]@@@@        @   @E@@@@        IF DEBUG? WRITE = 'NOWME
)@@G@@ @ADDING FILE "$$ETC1$"',*    @B@@@@        LET CSF = CSF ('@ADD,L $$ETCMF
)@@G@@1$.') @]@@@@        @   @ @@@@        @ THAT'S ALL FOLKS    @]@@@@      MG
)@@G@@  @   @]@@@@        STOP@]@@@@        @   @C@@@@SLNFG:  WRITE = '"ETC" IMH
)@@G@@NTERNAL ERROR 3.',*     @]@@@@        STOP@]@@@@        @   @G@@@@SINFG:MI
)@@G@@  ERROR                                  @ CAN'T READ SI FILE     @ @@@@MJ
)@@G@@        WRITE SIFORM <SI$>    @A@@@@        LET LEV=8 @ ASSUME LEVEL 8  MK
)@@G@@@A@@@@        GO TO BLDADD @ AND CONTINUE @]@@@@        @   @#@@@@EOF:  ML
)@@G@@  ERROR     @L@@@@        WRITE = 'END OF FILE ENCOUNTERED BEFORE SCHEMAMM
)@@G@@ NAME LOCATED. WILL ABORT JOB VIA "@ABORT"',*   @B@@@@        LET CSF = MN
)@@G@@CSF('@ASG,T $$ETC1$.')  @D@@@@        IF CSF<0 WRITE,S = '"ETC" INTERNALMO
)@@G@@ ERROR 1.',*@A@@@@        OPEN SDFO $$ETC1$=$$ETC1$.  @H@@@@        WRITMP
)@@G@@E = '@ABORT- . *** ABORT JOBSTREAM IF SCHEMA NAME NOT LOCATED!'   @H@@@@MQ
)@@G@@        PUT $$ETC1$ *                                @ PROCESSOR CALL LIMR
)@@G@@NE    @ @@@@        IF DEBUG? WRITE *     @#@@@@        WRITE = R @C@@@@MS
)@@G@@        GOTO CLOSE1 @ CLOSE $$ETC1$ AND @ADD IT @]@@@@        @   @J@@@@MT
)@@G@@ @      WRITE = 'END OF FILE ENCOUNTERED BEFORE SCHEMA NAME LOCATED. LEVMU
)@@G@@EL 8 ASSUMED.',*  @A@@@@ @      LET LEV=8 @ ASSUME LEVEL 8  @A@@@@ @    MV
)@@G@@  GO TO BLDADD @ AND CONTINUE _@@@@@^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)MW
)@@G@@^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)^@)*[S@@@*SDFF*@]@@@@*DBE-0MX

)@@G@@  @                                               @   @E@@@@        @***YV
)@@G@@********************************************@   @D@@@@            LET IXYW
)@@G@@ENTS = PH[3]:H1 @ NUMBER OF ENTRIES @E@@@@            LET IXLEN = PH[7]:YX
)@@G@@H1 @ LENGTH OF EACH ENTRY     @G@@@@            LET IXTOT = IXENTS * IXLYY
)@@G@@EN @ TOTAL SPACE USED FOR INDEXES   @C@@@@            WRITE IXENTS IXTOTYZ
)@@G@@,IXENTS,IXLEN     @K@@@@IXENTS:     FORMAT C16,'INDEX ENTRIES',C36,D4,' ZA
)@@G@@WORDS = ',D,' ENTRIES @ ',D,' WORDS EACH',*     @A@@@@          ELSE @ IZB
)@@G@@NDEX TRAILER PAGE @B@@@@            LET IXTOT = 0 @ FOR NOW !     @#@@@@ZC
)@@G@@          END IF  @E@@@@        @***************************************ZD
)@@G@@********@   @E@@@@        @                                             ZE
)@@G@@  @   @E@@@@        @ UNUSED SPACE                                  @   ZF
)@@G@@@E@@@@        @                                               @   @E@@@@ZG
)@@G@@        @***********************************************@   @B@@@@      ZH
)@@G@@    WRITE = C16,'UNUSED SPACE',C36  @A@@@@          LET UNUSED = PH[2]:HZI
)@@G@@2     @C@@@@          IF UNUSED <> 0 THEN @ UNUSED EXISTS   @B@@@@      ZJ
)@@G@@      WRITE UNUSED UNUSED,10+IXTOT  @E@@@@UNUSED:     FORMAT D4,' WORDS ZK
)@@G@@STARTING AT ADDRESS ',O,*     @#@@@@          END IF  @#@@@@        END ZL
)@@G@@IF    @E@@@@        @***********************************************@   ZM
)@@G@@@E@@@@        @                                               @   @E@@@@ZN

)@@G@@@]@@@@        @   @E@@@@        @***************************************ZT
)@@G@@********@   @E@@@@        @                                             ZU

)@@G@@ATCHED WITH DMU!',*     @#@@@@        END IF    @]@@@@        @   @E@@@@AA
)@@G@@        @***********************************************@   @E@@@@      AB

)@@G@@LC CHAIN ZERO                               @   @E@@@@        @         AD

)@@G@@  @   @B@@@@          WRITE = C12,'CALC CHAIN 0 '     @ @@@@          IFAJ
)@@G@@ PH[7] = 0 THEN   @A@@@@            WRITE = 'IS UNUSED',*   @#@@@@      AK
)@@G@@    ELSE    @B@@@@            LET <APR> = DECODE(PH[7])     @A@@@@      AL
)@@G@@      IF APR(1) = ACODE THEN  @E@@@@              IF APR(2) = PGNUM THENAM

)@@G@@2)    @E@@@@F7B:            FORMAT 'POINTS TO PAGE ',D,', PGSLOT ',D,*  AR
)@@G@@@^@@@@              END IF    @A@@@@            ELSE @ DIFFERENT AREA   AS

)@@G@@AT 'POINTS TO AREA ',D,', PAGE ',D,', PGSLOT ',D@#@@@@            END IFAU
)@@G@@@#@@@@          END IF  @#@@@@        END IF    @E@@@@        @*********AV
)@@G@@**************************************@   @E@@@@        @               AW

)@@G@@ LET POWER(126)='@@@@@['@[@@@@ @    @A@@@@ DIM IN(2),ACCUM(2),PWR(2),RSLDZ
)@@G@@T(3)  @ @@@@ @ LET IN(1)=0000067405553    @ @@@@ @ LET IN(2)=01647307777EA

)@@G@@ LET <ACCUM>=ALL(0)     @B@@@@ REPEAT BIT=0,1 @ START FROM THE RIGHT    EC
)@@G@@@^@@@@   IF [IN:72-BIT,1] THEN@B@@@@     LET P=125-2*BIT @ INDEX INTO POED
)@@G@@WER() @F@@@@     LET <PWR>=<POWER:P,P+1> @ COPY VALUE FOR 2**BIT INTO <PEE
)@@G@@WR>   @G@@@@     REPEAT I=18,-1 @ WORK FROM LAST 4-BIT SET ON THE RIGHT EF
)@@G@@TO THE LEFT @E@@@@       LET S=[ACCUM:I,4]+[PWR:I,4]+CARRY @ ADD A COLUMEG
)@@G@@N     @B@@@@       LET CARRY=S>9 @ COMPUTE CARRY VALUE@D@@@@       LET [EH
)@@G@@ACCUM:I,4]=S\10 @ & NEW ACCUMULATOR DIGIT @#@@@@     UNTIL I=1    @]@@@@EI
)@@G@@   END IF   @#@@@@ UNTIL BIT=60     @A@@@@ REPEAT I=1,1 @ LOOP THRU 18 DEJ
)@@G@@IGITS @C@@@@   LET [RSLT:I,6]=[ACCUM:I,4]+060 @ MAKE IT FD  @]@@@@ UNTILEK
)@@G@@ I=18 @ @@@@ @ 3F6: FORMAT '"',<3>F6,'"',*@^@@@@ @ WRITE 3F6 <RSLT>     EL
)@@G@@@#@@@@ RETURN <RSLT>    _@@@@@DIGIT @#@@@@     UNTIL I=1    @]@@@@   ENDEM
